{"tid":1606142,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非新戰線]啱啱收到房委會嘅信，大家幫手舉報濫用公屋","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T18:53:47.000Z","uid":110851,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e3fb194108c9d3c4222c7e1371485bce9ae604a","tid":1606142,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2JxObuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2JxObuk.jpg&h=1d853755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說啱啱去信箱拎信<br />\n真香港人冇屋住真係好慘，點解d狗可以住公屋<br />\n我記得公屋唔可以養狗架<br />\n大家身邊有冇狗係公屋住？<br />\n我老豆搵到d狗仔係公屋住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係時候一齊去舉報喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收唔到信/冇機會收到呢封信都唔緊要<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/public-housing/tenancy-matters/combating-housing-abuses/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic-housing%2Ftenancy-matters%2Fcombating-housing-abuses%2Findex.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6qVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=a70ef40a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/public-housing/tenancy-matters/combating-housing-abuses/index.html</a><br />\n以上嘅link都可以report"},{"pid":"9858145479f053cc4257897df266aebc4e88c56f","tid":1606142,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:19:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a26fa8eb49ce8c37ded9ae30d7d3fdd70dc90200","tid":1606142,"uid":12468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:20:21.000Z","msg":"一齊舉報濫用資源嘅狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57460c1babdf52ee4193516892fe42678cfde21e","tid":1606142,"uid":110851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a26fa8eb49ce8c37ded9ae30d7d3fdd70dc90200","tid":1606142,"uid":12468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T1